title: Electricity prices for households in Spain 2010 - 2018 , semi-annually
summary: Overall Euro cents per kilowatt-hour has increased over the Year.
Euro cents per kilowatt-hour is slightly increasing from 2013_S2 to 2014_S2, and finally roughly constant from 2014_S2 to 2015_S1.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2014_S1 and 2014_S2.
The highest Euro cents per kilowatt-hour, of value 23.67 was reached at Year 2014_S2
The lowest Euro cents per kilowatt-hour, of value 21.65 was reported at Year 2014_S1
min_summary: In general Euro cents per kilowatt-hour has stayed the same over the Year.
